{"tid":758973,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人試過因為唔想俾人聞到，聞返晒自己啲屁","createTime":"2018-07-28T07:37:13.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-28T14:15:34.000Z","uid":142518,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"9bad90b0a992ea90ddcafc1a1baa12627afda379","tid":758973,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:37:13.000Z","msg":"以前中學嘅時候，<br />\n有陣時feel到想放屁<br />\n就會死忍唔放出嚟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但如果真係唔小心放咗出嚟<br />\n仲要係極臭嗰隻無聲屁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我就會襯啲屁未飄過去同學嗰邊<br />\n用力咁索返自己啲屁<br />\n希望唔好俾同學聞到懷疑係我放屁<br />\n尤其是附近有女同學<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n而家諗返起又覺得啲屁幾好聞<br />\n簡直係極致嘅嗅覺享受<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"00d32bf331c807b2dce7714a95be086865d98ed2","tid":758973,"uid":123456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"巴打好細心<br />\n好想0距離聞你啲屁<br />\n可唔可以順便泌小小屎汁比我奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"973eab1572e6a3a2bafb5aa031c6fcbec356bd9b","tid":758973,"uid":3647,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:40:52.000Z","msg":"從來係吝惜過<br />\n亦會認<br />\n大大力放出黎<br />\n響既我d frd 都知係我<br />\n臭既會單聲"},{"pid":"dfdb82cc625cfe2397e81b69070a0f7863534828","tid":758973,"uid":183194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:42:43.000Z","msg":"咁短時間好高難度"},{"pid":"052048629331b4bc23a705e1441af364a49ee1eb","tid":758973,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dfdb82cc625cfe2397e81b69070a0f7863534828","tid":758973,"uid":183194,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:42:43.000Z","msg":"咁短時間好高難度"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:46:56.000Z","msg":"所以曾經比女同學見到我用力索嘅樣<br />\n我發現嘅時候，佢已經掩住咗個鼻<br />\n之後唔知點解成個中學生涯都冇女仔坐我隔離<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"380eb69b6437d48d70b2a2bec82be87b7af55d72","tid":758973,"uid":188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:48:10.000Z","msg":"隔離有人會專登大力小小放"},{"pid":"7a158c762a3266a3b331646636fe5efb0e7e7379","tid":758973,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00d32bf331c807b2dce7714a95be086865d98ed2","tid":758973,"uid":123456,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:38:35.000Z","msg":"巴打好細心<br />\n好想0距離聞你啲屁<br />\n可唔可以順便泌小小屎汁比我奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T07:48:18.000Z","msg":"一齊互奶又點話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"993f3fd634352b621b535eebf557b3736370cea7","tid":758973,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T09:06:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff766d1fb5717613d2855f3bb571c3b44cadf200","tid":758973,"uid":142518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-28T14:15:34.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}